Umubare w'abandura COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, 1 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020
Uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, byerekana ko nubwo ibihe bigenda bitandukana bitewe n'ibihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Nk'uko byibonekeye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bugarijwe n'indwara z'ibyorezo bigomba kongera imbaraga mu guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bwihariye n'ubuvuzi bw'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya Sisu cy'impamvu zitazwi cyatangajwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatangaje ko icyateye iyi ndwara ari coronavirus nshya, ubu ikaba izwi ku izina rya coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa 2 y'indwara ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero yitwa 2-SARS-CoV.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara y'icyorezo iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yitwa COVID-19.
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko 80% by'abandura COVID-19 bagira ibibazo byoroheje, ni ukuvuga guhumeka nabi, cyangwa guhumeka nabi, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
14% by'abandura COVID-19 bagomba kujyanwa mu bitaro, naho 6% by'abandura COVID-19 bagomba kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye.
Abanduye COVID-19 bafite igipimo cyo gupfa kingana na 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turiga imiterere y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Ubulayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza, hanyuma tukagereranya imiterere n'ubwandu mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EAE n'u Bwongereza n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EAEAU na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yageze no mu bindi bihugu, ndetse n'ibindi bihugu ku isi byakurikije urugero rw'icyorezo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyabaye icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri n'abo bafatanyije nk'uko bisobanurwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, batangaje ko ari bo ba mbere bemeje ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi.
Mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Umuryango w'Ubushinwa, abanduye batatu ba mbere bemeje ko banduye batangajwe ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyari kimaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, aho kugeza ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 hari hamaze kwandura abantu 39,768, harimo 1,727 bapfuye, muri bo abagera ku 17,750, naho 1,441 bapfa mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubara umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'umubare w'abanduye
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), gitangaza ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura COVID-19 ku isi uturuka ku makuru y'ibanze nk'ayo ibigo by'ubuzima byo mu bihugu, abayobozi bo mu nzego z'ubuvuzi zo mu turere n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritanga, kandi ko buri munsi rigenda rivugururwa saa munani z'ijoro.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma ibipimo bya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, hagereranywa n'iby'u Butaliyani.
Nk'uko twabibonye mu bushakashatsi ku mibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, twahereye ku mibare y'iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri rusange, bityo twerekana uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye muri buri gihugu cya EU no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twanatanze kandi umubare w'abamaze kwandura muri buri gihugu kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo ku ya 15 Werurwe, ugereranyije n'umubare w'abamaze kwandura mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe.
Uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye mu bihugu bigize EU no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, muri rusange, ikurikije iy'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1.1).
Mu bihugu bigize umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku ya 21 Gashyantare, buzamuka cyane ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ku kigereranyo).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bw'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza na byo byagize ukwiyongera nk'uko mu mibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byabo.
Igishushanyo cya 2 cyerekana imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi bigaragaza ko guhera saa munani z'igitondo ku ya 15 Werurwe, umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu 15 by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza wari ungana n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 cyangwa bitarenzeho.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza wiyongereye cyane.
Imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko ubwandu buri kugenda buzamuka ku kigero kimwe mu bihugu byose.
Ibi birimo kuba ibihugu biri mu bihe bitandukanye kandi bidahuza mu buryo bw'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange, ndetse no gutandukanya ibisobanuro by'imibare y'abanduye n'uburyo bwo gupima abarwayi kugira ngo hamenyekane niba baranduye COVID-19.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu duce tw'u Butaliyani bagaragaje ko hafi 10% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho byihutirwa, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihutirwa muri utwo duce byageze ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Amaperereza y'uko abarwayi ba COVID-19 baherekejwe mu bitaro cyangwa mu byumba by'indembe mu bihugu bigize umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi, ubu ni 6% na 1% by'abarwayi gusa (ntabwo ayo makuru agaragazwa).
Icyakora, ayo makuru agomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo amakuru y'ubugenzuzi yibanze ku mubare w'abantu banditswe n'umubare w'abapfuye ashobore kuzura.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Ugushyingo 2010 bwerekanye itandukaniro rinini ry'ibitanda biboneka mu bitaro by'indembe n'iby'imiti mu Burayi, aho mu Budage hari ibitanda 29.2 na 4.2 ku bantu 100.000 mu Butaliyani na Porutugali.
Ibi byerekana ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite amikoro make cyangwa menshi ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (12.5 ibitanda byo kwa muganga ku bantu 100,000 mu Ugushyingo 2020).
Imigaragambyo yo kugenzura iherekejwe n'ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ibipimo by'indwara ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, bifatwa nk'ibishyize hejuru ku buryo bishobora gutuma ibitanda by'abarwayi ba ICU byongerwa ubushobozi ku rugero rusaga 90%, byatangajwe mu bushakashatsi bwa ECDC kuri COVID-19 bwahise bukorwa vuba vuba.
Kubera ko ubwandu mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza bwigwizaho, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima bifasha abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru ajyanye n'ubwandu n'ibigo nderabuzima birushaho kuba byiza gufatwa mu magambo y'ibarurwa ry'ibice by'ibanze by'imibare y'icyiciro cya 2.
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibibera mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira vuba mu bihugu bigize EU no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'indera byihutirwa bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'uko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukomeza kwandura mu baturage, ndetse n'uko umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 bashobora kwiyongera, bagakenera kwitabwaho mu nzego z'ubuvuzi, bamwe muri bo bakaba bagomba kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye, nk'uko bimeze mu bihugu by'u Butaliyani birimo kwandura.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'igenzura ry'ibyago ryihuta rya vuba na ECDC, hakenewe uburyo bwihuse kandi bwihuse bwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya coronavirus ya SARS-CoV-2, hamwe no guhindura uburyo bwo gukumira bukagenda bugabanuka, kubera ko bitewe n'uko umubare w'abanduye ugiye kwiyongera vuba, nta gihe gihagije abashinzwe kugenzura no ku bitaro bafite cyo gusobanukirwa, guhuza no guhuza ibisubizo byabo kandi birashoboka ko batagomba gutinda.
Igenzura ry'ibyago ryihuse kandi rivuga ko ingamba zo kwita ku buzima rusange zigomba gufatwa kugira ngo hakumirwe ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Ubu hari igihe gito ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya umutwaro ku buzima.
Biramutse ari byo, cyangwa bigatsindwa, gahunda y'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu bigize EU ishobora kuzahura n'ubwandu mu minsi cyangwa ibyumweru biri imbere, bukenera kwitabwaho cyane.
Icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ifata mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ya SARS-CoV-2 (coronavirus), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu ku isi, kikaba cyanduje abagera ku 80,000.
Kimwe n'izindi koronavirusi zisa nka SARS-CoV, yanduje abantu ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yandujwe n'imbeba kandi ikaba ishobora kugira imikorere isa n'iy'imbeba, bityo igatanga ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Nubwo ubukana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ari bike ugereranyije na SARS, ubwandu bwayo burakabije kandi yibasira abantu bakuze n'abagabo cyane kurusha urubyiruko n'abagore.
Iki kiganiro cyatanzwe mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo gishya cyadutse, gitanga isesengura ryimbitse kandi ryimbitse ku buryo bwihuse mu gihe ubushakashatsi bugikomeje gukorwa.
Tugiye kuvuga ku ngingo z'ingenzi z'ubuvuzi, impamvu z'indwara, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kubara no kwirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye gusubizwa, twizeye ko iri sesengura rizadufasha gusobanukirwa no kwirinda iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'isura wo ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rudasanzwe ku bantu bo mu Bushinwa kubera ko bari bategetswe kumara ibyumweru byinshi mu rugo kandi bakajya mu biruhuko nyuma y'icyorezo gishya cya virusi.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje SARS mu 2003; niyo mpamvu OMS ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 yise coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 n'indwara yayikomotseho COVID-19.
Iki cyorezo cyaturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze kiza gukwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iki cyorezo cyamaze kwandura abantu 80.000, abagera ku 40.000 barakira naho abagera ku 3.000 barapfa.
OMS iravuga ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere ku isi" ufite imbaraga ziruta iz'iterabwoba.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na PubMed ((https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, hasohotse inyandiko zirenga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19 mu byerekeranye na viroloji, patoloji, indwara, gusuzuma no kuvura iki cyorezo kuva inkuru yambere yatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 kandi bagaragaje urusobe rwa virusi mu barwayi benshi batandukanye.
Iyi raporo igaragaza ko ubushakashatsi muri iki cyiciro cy'ubushakashatsi buri kugenda kizamuka mu buryo bwihuse.
Iyo bigaragaye, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na koronavirusi, ndetse na MERS (Middle East Respiratory Syndrome, pandemic yo mu wa 2012).
Tuzabagezaho ibyo tuzi ku bijyanye no kwirinda no kumenya uko umuntu yabyitwaramo, ndetse n'ibibazo byihutirwa bitarasubizwa.
Coronaviruses ni virusi isanzwe ifata abantu mu buryo butari bwo kandi ishobora gutera ibyorezo bigera kuri 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'indwara ebyiri z'ibyorezo z'abantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, maze zikwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi ku isi mu gihe gito, bituma habaho umubare utangaje w'abanduye n'abapfa.
Ni ukuvuga ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus cyabayeho mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe ku ishusho ya 1.1, ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ifite inkomoko idatangazwa byatangajwe bwa mbere n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima mu Bushinwa, Wuhan, ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
