Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere yishwe muri Wuhan.
Muri icyo gihe, icyorezo cyakwirakwijwe mu mijyi, mu ntara no mu bihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cy'ibicurane cyamenyekanye mu bakozi b'ubuzima, kandi cyerekana ko iyi ndwara ishobora gukwirakwira mu bantu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizwe mu kato, kandi ingendo zose za rusange zarahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Ukuboza, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'abaganga bwahishuye ko mu bantu 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ni bo bahuye n'isoko rya porogaramu y'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, bityo iki cyorezo kikaba ari cyo cya mbere cyatewe n'inyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryashyize ahagaragara ikibazo cy'indwara y'ibyorezo ku isi.
Kugeza igihe iyi raporo yandikiwe, iki cyorezo cyari cyakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda birushaho kuba bibi, nta cyemezo gifatika gifatwa ku birebana n'uko isi izarangira.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8.866, bwerekanye ko abantu 4.021 bafite icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe, hagaragazwa ishusho nshya y'ubwandu muri rusange (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduye abantu bari mu myaka yose, ariko abenshi bari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
