Mu Kuboza 2019, icyorezo cya koronavirusi nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV) cyatangiye gukwirakwira, ubu kikaba cyiswe byemewe n'amategeko indwara iterwa na koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-2019) ndetse n'indwara yiswe SARS-CoV-2 (Coronavirus 2nd Stage Respiratory Syndrome).
