Nk'uko byasobanuwe mu cyiciro cya 7 (Gatanu 3, 2020), kugira ngo hamenyekane niba hari umuntu ukekwaho kuba arwaye, buri kintu kigaragaza amateka y'icyorezo kigomba guhuzwa n'ibintu bibiri by'ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura ryimbitse, cyangwa ibintu bitatu by'ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga niba amateka y'icyorezo ataramenyekana neza:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) Amateka yo gutembera cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu tundi turere aho abantu bagaragaye ko banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko bagaragaza ibimenyetso; (2) Amateka yo guhura n'umuntu urwaye SARS-CoV-2 (yakoze ibizamini bya aside aside ya nikeleyeri igaragaza ko yanduye); (3) Amateka yo guhura n'umuntu ufite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa abandi bantu bagaragaye ko banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko bagaragaza ibimenyetso; (4) Amateka yo guhura n'abantu benshi banduye (>= 2 bagaragaye n'abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu mu turere duto, nko mu ngo, mu biro, mu mashuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) kurwara birimo ibimenyetso by'indwara ya COVID-19; (3) umubare w'umusemburo w'umweru ugaragaza umubare usanzwe, wagabanutse, cyangwa wagabanutse w'uturemangingo tw'umubiri mu cyiciro cya mbere cya Zika.
Gushyiraho icyemezo cy'uko umuntu arwaye byashingira ku kuba hari ibimenyetso by'uburwayi cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi bw'ubwonko bikurikira: (1) igihe habonetse umusaruro mwiza wa PCR wa SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe nyacyo; (2) igihe habonetse virusi ifite ubwoko butandukanye bw'indwara ya koronavirusi nshya; (3) igihe habonetse udukingirizo twa IgM n'utw'umubiri twitwa IgG tuzana SARS-CoV-2 mu gupima umusaruro w'umusemburo; cyangwa igihe IgG tuzana SARS-CoV-2 ihindutse ikorana n'uburwayi, cyangwa igihe =>4 y'umubiri w'umuntu yongeye kuba mwiza mu gihe cy'uburwayi.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo byafashwe ku bipimo bya nucleic acid mu mwuka cyangwa mu maraso byongerewe ku mpapuro ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) na mpapuro ya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Gusuzuma indwara mu bipimo by'amaraso byongewe mu gice cya kane (tariki ya 27 Mutarama 2020) no mu gice cya gatanu (tariki ya 8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu mitsi yo mu nda byongewe mu gice cya karindwi.
