Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 - indwara iterwa na koronavirusi yitwa SARS-CoV-2 - cyakwiriye ku isi hose.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekana gusa uko indwara yandura, aho kwerekana ingamba zihariye umuntu ashobora gufata, OMS ivuga ko leta igomba gufata ingamba zikurikira:
Umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Ibihugu byasuzuma abaturage babyo, bikabakorakora, bikabakorakoranya, bikabakurikirana, bikanga kubaha ibisubizo.
Dufite impungenge z'uko iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye cyane, kandi kikaba gikomeye, ndetse n'uko kitakiriho.
Tom Friedan, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no kurinda indwara, yavuze ko icyorezo "kitarimo ubufasha".
Yagize ati, nk'uko CNN yabitangaje mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, "uretse ibicurane, nta bindi byorezo by'iby'ubuhumekero byakurikiranwe kuva bigitangira kugeza ubu bikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi".
Gebryus yavuze ko na we ari uko, agira ati "ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "Kandi nta cyorezo na kimwe twigeze tubona cyashoboraga guhangana n'iki cyorezo icyarimwe".
Iki cyorezo cy'isi gishya kije gikurikira icyemezo cya OMS cyo gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ihutirwa ku isi mu kwezi kwa mbere, gihangayikishije isi yose.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe indwara zandura, Dr Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko "muri make, ibintu bigenda birushaho kuba bibi".
