Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi cya 2019-20 ni icyorezo gikomeje kubaho cya Koronavirusi (COVID-19) iterwa n'indwara ikomeye yo mu buhumekero iterwa na Koronavirusi ya 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Kuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'indwara z'ibanze ku isi tariki 30 Mutarama 2020, maze cyemezwa nk'icyorezo cyugarije isi yose tariki 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri 1.61 miliyoni banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu n'uturere 210, bituma abagera ku 97,000 bapfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Umubare w'abapfa ugereranywa na 4% mu Bushinwa, naho isi yose ugereranywa na 13.04% uhereye muri Alijeriya ukagera kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni impumuro mbi, guhekenya no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora kuba byatewe n'uburwayi bw'umura, guhumeka nabi, cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Akenshi bimara iminsi itanu, ariko bishobora no kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza kuri cumi n'ine.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti uvura virusi bizwi.
Gahunda z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara zirimo gukaraba intoki, kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe cy'indwara, kwirinda kwegerana n'abandi, gukurikiranwa no kwitandukanya n'abandi mu gihe umuntu akekwaho kuba yaranduye.
Ku isi hose, abayobozi bagiye babikora bashyiraho ingamba zo gukumira ingendo, gushyirwa mu kato, guhagarika ingendo, kugenzura ibijyanye n'ibyago, no gufunga ibikorwa.
Icyorezo cyateye ihungabana ry'imibereho y'abaturage ku isi, gusubika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa by'imikino, amadini, politiki n'umuco, no gukena kw'ibikoresho byinshi biturutse ku kugura ibintu byinshi.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu karere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99.4% cy'abanyeshuri ku isi.
Amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri iyi virusi yakwirakwiye ku mbuga za interineti, ndetse n'ibikorwa byo gutinya abanyamahanga no kuvangura Abashinwa, abandi bantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba n'Amajyepfo y'uburasirazuba bw'Ubushinwa, n'abandi bantu bo mu turere turimo iyi virusi.
Kubera ko ingendo zagabanyijwe kandi inganda zikomeye zigakurwaho, hashobora kuboneka ihinduka rikomeye mu guhumanya ikirere no mu mwuka wangiza ikirere.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari abantu benshi banduye indwara y'ibihaha ku ya 31 Mutarama 2019, batangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Benshi mu banduye bagaragaye mu masoko yo mu Buhinde acuruza ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, bityo iki cyorezo kikaba gishobora kuba gikomoka ku nyamaswa.
Virusi yateye iki cyorezo yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni virusi nshya yavumbuwe ifitanye isano na coronavirus yo mu bwoko bw'ingona, coronavirus yo mu bwoko bw'ingona, SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yagize ibimenyetso byayo, akaba yanduye ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama 2019, nta sano afitanye n'umuryango w'abacuruzi b'inyama.
Muri izo mpfu zavuzwe bwa mbere mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'inyama.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itavuzwe ukuri mu kinyamakuru South China Morning Post yavuze ko umuntu umwe wanduye tariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, ni umukecuru w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ashobora kuba ari we wa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko, n'ubwo ubwandu bushya bwagabanutse mu Bushinwa, ariko bukazamuka mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani, na Koreya y'Epfo, ku nshuro ya mbere umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye mu Bushinwa.
