Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare munini w'abandura bari bakiri bato, bafite imyaka 19 n'abari munsi yayo, ni ukuvuga 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Patrick Vallance, umujyanama mu by'ubumenyi mu Bwongereza, avuga ko 60% by'abatuye u Bwongereza bashobora kuba baranduye mbere y'uko ubudahangarwa bw'abantu benshi bugera ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga banduye COVID-19, kandi bapimwe bagasanga baranduye hakurikijwe amabwiriza y'ubuziranenge.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoresheje ibizamini ku bantu barenze 3% by'abaturage, kandi ibihugu byinshi byari bifite politiki yo kutemera abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, u Busuwisi na Esipanye.
