Imibare y'abantu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 ishobora kuba iri hejuru cyane, kubera ko ishobora kuba ari iy'abantu bapfuye bari mu kato - urugero, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru, n'ibindi.
