Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba byinshi ku buryo nta muntu wabasha kubibona, kandi abantu banduye bashobora no kutagira ibimenyetso.
Bimwe mu bimenyetso bikunze kugaragara cyane ni impumuro mbi ku kigero cya 88% na kanseri (68%).
Ibindi bimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara ni uburibwe, guhumeka nabi, kubura uburyo bwo guhumeka, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo, kuruka, kubabara, guhinda, gusohora amaraso, kuva amaraso mu gihe wagize ikibazo cy'igicuri, kuruka, cyangwa guhinduka ibara. Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) rivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara indwara y'ubuhumekero kandi akaba afite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no kurinda indwara (CDC) cyasobanuye ko ibimenyetso by'indwara ya asthmatic ari ibibazo byo guhumeka, kubabara cyangwa guhora uhuha, guhora unuka, kunanirwa kugenda, no kugira amaso cyangwa iminwa itukura; hakenewe ubuvuzi bwihuse niba ufite ibyo bimenyetso.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba batagaragaza ibimenyetso, nta kimenyetso kigaragara, ariko ibizamini byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagasaba ko abantu bose bahuye n'abanduye bakwirindwa cyane, kandi bagasaba ko bakorerwa isuku kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Ubushinwa buvuga ko nta kimenyetso na kimwe cy'iyo ndwara kiboneka, ariko ko buvuga ko kizaba ari 44% by'abo barwaye.
