Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi ishyiraho ibihano ku kugura ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi ku bwinshi. Kimwe n'u Bwongereza na Amerika, byerekana ko kugabanya (gukomeza gukwirakwiza icyorezo aho kugihagarika) no guhagarika (guhagarika icyorezo) bigira ibibazo bikomeye.
Gahunda nziza zo kugabanya ubwandu zishobora kugabanya umubare w'abajya kwa muganga ku kigero cya 2/3 n'icy'abapfa ku kigero cya 50%. Nyamara kandi, bishobora no guteza impfu zibarirwa mu bihumbi amagana no gusenya inganda z'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba byiza, ariko bikwiye gukomeza kugeza igihe virusi izava mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari ubwa mbere), kubera ko ubwandu bushobora kwiyongera mugihe ingamba zidakorwa.
Gahunda z'igihe kirekire zo gukumira icyorezo ziteza ibibazo mu bukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage.
Nta muti wihariye uvura COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa biri gukorwa, harimo no gupima imiti isanzwe iriho.
Kunywa imiti igabanya imbeho, kunywa amazi menshi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso byayo.
Dukurikije uko umurwayi yiyumva, imiti ya ogisijeni, indimu yo mu mitsi, no gufasha guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Gukoresha imiti yo kwangiza uruhu bishobora gutuma ingaruka zirushaho kuba mbi.
Hari imiti myinshi yari yaremejwe mbere yo kuvura izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko "uburyo bwo kuvurwa mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga" bushobora gutuma ibimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-19 bigabanuka.
Umuryango Mpuzamahanga w'Ubuzima (WHO) wagaragaje ko kwihutisha serivisi z'ubuvuzi ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ari uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere k'umuryango w'abibumbye by'ubuzima (OMS) byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo haboneke uburyo bwo kuvura ku nzego nyinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu byo gukoresha mu mavuriro hagamijwe gupima COVID-19, kwanga gukoresha uburyo bw'ubuvuzi igihe cyose bishoboka, gushyira mu kato abanduye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi cyane cyane binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zo guhumeka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'aho icyorezo cya mbere (cyitwa indwara ya 0) cyakomotse.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwi wanduye coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yaranduye ku ya 1 Mutarama 2019, i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye cyane.
Byinshi muri byo byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu mazi rya Huang, aho bagurishaga n'amatungo ari nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yaturutse kuri kimwe muri ibyo biribwa; cyangwa, mu bundi buryo, ko ifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa. Impamvu itaramenyekana y'indwara y'ibicurane yagaragaye ku ya 26 Mutarama, ivurwa na Dr. Zhang Jixan wo mu bitaro by'akarere ka Hubei, wari wabwiye CDC ko hari igicuruzwa cy'agakoko k'inzoka cyabaye i Wuhan ku ya 27 Mutarama.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru by'i Wuhan bamenyesheje bagenzi babo ko "hari virusi ya korona imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, bari barahawe amabwiriza akomeye n'abapolisi kubera ko bakwirakwije poropagande mbi, naho undi, Ai Feng, we yari yaratewe ubwoba n'umuyobozi we kubera ko yari yarongereye ingengabitekerezo y'ibyago.
Nyuma y'aho, Komisiyo y'ubuzima ya Wuhan yatangiye ibikorwa byo gutanga inama rusange ku ya 31 Mutarama, kandi yatangarije OMS ko hari ikibazo cy'uburwayi cyabayeho.
Abantu benshi banduye indwara y'impyiko idasobanutse batangajwe n'abashinzwe ubuzima i Wuhan kugira ngo batangize iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu byiciro bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro na hagati za Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu tundi duce two mu Bushinwa, ibifashijwemo n'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa n'umuhanda wa gari ya moshi uri mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, u Bushinwa bwatangaje ko bwagize abandi bantu bashya 140 banduye, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe muri Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe ahita agaragaza ko kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu bagera ku 6174 bari baranduye. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yageze ku mwanya wa mbere nyuma y'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani mu kugira umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi.
Hari ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byabonetsemo nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera iki cyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ingendo z'abantu ku giti cyabo kandi bishyiraho uburyo bwo kugenzura imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu cyagaragaje ingamba zo kwirinda nka karantini (zitwa amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo gufungira abantu mu byumba, cyangwa amabwiriza yo gufungira abantu mu ngo) no gufunga imihanda. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, ni ukuvuga hafi 90% y'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bwo kuguma mu rugo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu basaga miliyoni 50 bari mu rugo muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu rugo muri Afurika y'Epfo, naho 1.3 muri bo bari mu rugo mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi baguma mu rugo mu buryo runaka, naho mu minsi ibiri yakurikiyeho, bariyongereyeho miriyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yagaragaye muri Wuhan ku ya 1 Mutarama 2019; raporo imwe itazwi neza igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye COVID-19 yagaragaye muri Wuhan ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Dr. Zhang Jixun yavuze ko hari umuntu umwe ufite ikibazo cy'impyiko z'igifu ku itariki ya 26 Mutarama, bituma ibitaro bya Wuhan bimenyesha CDC ku itariki ya 27 Mutarama.
Igenzura rya mbere ryakozwe ku baganga mu bagore barwaye SARS ku ya 27 Mutarama 2019 ryagaragaje ko hari ubwoko bwa koronavirusi busa n'ubw'icyorezo cya SARS.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan yashyize ahagaragara itangazo rigenewe rubanda.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryabwiwe iby'iki cyorezo mu gitondo cyo kuri uyu wa Gatatu.
Mu gihe iyi mpanuka yabaga, abaganga bo muri Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo na polisi ku 'propaganda' y'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje gutangaza ko nta "buhamya busobanutse" bw'uko umuntu yajyanwa ku wundi.
Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa mbere, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangiye ubukangurambaga bwiswe "Intambara y'abaturage" n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'ishyaka ry'Abashinwa ry'Abakomunisiti, mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu byiswe "karantine ikomeye mu mateka y'abantu", ku ya 23 Mutarama, hafunguwe itegeko ribuza ingendo zijya cyangwa ziva mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ryatangijwe mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, bigera ku bantu miliyoni 57.
Imodoka zigenga ntizemewe gutwara abantu mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (25 Mutarama) byarabuzanyijwe mu turere twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko imirimo yo kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro by'ubwishingizi, yarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma y'aho, iyindi bitaro, Ishami rya Lishechsan, ryubatswe kugira ngo rivurwe izindi ndwara.
Usibye ibitaro bishya, u Bushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'inama n'ibibuga by'imikino, bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo guhagarika itangazamakuru ry'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kongera igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'isura.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Uturere twa Hong Kong na Macao twafashe ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku mashuri na kaminuza.
Ibikoresho byo gukora kure byatangiye gukoreshwa mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa.
Ingendo z'abari mu gihugu n'abari hanze zarasubitswe.
Ingendo rusange zarahagaritswe, kandi amazu ndangamurage mu Bushinwa hose yarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu gihe ingendo rusange zatangiraga gukurikizwa mu mijyi myinshi, byitezwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abasaga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bagombaga gukurikiza amabwiriza yo gufunga imihanda. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo cy'icyorezo cyateye mu rwego rw'isi muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo guhagarika "kwinjiza" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho igihe cy'iminsi 14 yo kuguma mu rugo ku ngendo z'amahanga zose zinjira mu mujyi.Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa hari habonetse umurwayi umwe gusa wa coronavirus mu minsi itanu, muri iki gihe hari umurwayi wavuye i Guangzhou muri Istanbul.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyamaze guhagarikwa burundu kandi ko cyakemuwe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo muri Hubei zarorohejwe, usibye Wuhan, amezi abiri nyuma yo gushyirwa mu kato. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira muri icyo gihugu kubera visa cyangwa gutunga uruhushya rwo gutura bizakorwa kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, nyuma yaho, nta bisobanuro byihariye ku gihe iryo tegeko rizarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa basabwa gusaba viza ku biro by'u Bushinwa by'ubuseruki n'ubuserukizi.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yasabye ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi n'inganda bifungurwa guhera ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku masosiyete. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo uzatangira n'isaha ya gatatu y'agahe gato ku isaha ya 10:00 ku ya 4 Mata, ihurirana n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo leta y'ibanze yasabye imiryango gukomeza gukurikiza gahunda yo kwirinda kwirinda kwirinda kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishya.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri Koreya y'Epfo cyemejwe ko cyaturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Gashyantare, Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima (NHA) cyatangaje ko hari ubwiyongere bw'abantu benshi, ahanini bitewe n'uko mu mujyi wa Daegu hari itorero ry'idini ryitwa Shinseong Church of Christ.
Abategetsi ba Shintonguj baje gusura Taiwan baturutse i Wuhan, bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye icyorezo cyakwirakwira.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9336 ba Kiliziya, 1,261, cyangwa hafi 13%, bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ingamba zo ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2000 bari bamaze kwandura muri Koreya, biyongeraho 3150 ku ya 29 Gashyantare.
Ingabo zose zo muri Koreya y'Epfo zahawe akato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bapimwe bagasanga banduye.
Byagize ingaruka ku ngengabihe y'indege, bituma zihinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ya mbere nini kandi nziza ku isi yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo barebe niba bafite virusi, gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bagaragayeho virusi.
Uburyo bwo gupima ubwabyo bwarimo gutanga raporo ku buryo bw'agateganyo ku bantu bavuye mu bindi bihugu bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima imodoka kugira ngo harebwe niba hari virusi, kandi ibisubizo bikaba byarashoboraga kuboneka umunsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugira ngo abantu 20,000 bapimwe buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'epfo ivuga ko ari igikorwa cyagenze neza mu guhashya icyorezo nubwo itaba iherereye mu mijyi yose. Umuryango wa Koreya y'epfo wigeze kugabanywamo ibice kubera uburyo Perezida Moon Jae-in yitabiriye icyo cyorezo.
Abanyekoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashyikirizwa ubutabera kubera ko bavuga ko leta itakoze neza mu kurwanya icyorezo, cyangwa bashima igisubizo bahawe.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ari yo ya mbere mu byumweru bine mu kugira abantu bake banduye mu munsi umwe.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko kuva ku ya 1 Mata, ingendo zose z'abanyamahanga zizashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabivuze ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yabonye ibyifuzo byo gufasha mu gupima virusi ya SARS mu bihugu 121.
Tariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Irani yatangaje ko hari umuntu wa mbere wanduye SARS-CoV-2 mu gihugu cya Qom, nyuma y'aho abaganga bo muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima bavuga ko hapfuye abantu babiri.
Ingamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, gusenga ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga za kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize muri gahunda miliyoni eshanu z'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ahantu habonetse icyorezo, abantu bonyine ni bo bashyirwa mu kato.
Muri Werurwe, hatangajwe ko hari gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi, nubwo ingendo nyinshi hagati y'imijyi zakomeje mbere y'umwaka mushya w'Abafarisayo.
Kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, insengero za Shia mu mujyi wa Qom zakomeje gufungurirwa abantu. Irani ni cyo gihugu cya mbere cyanduye iki cyorezo muri Gashyantare, nyuma y'Ubushinwa.
Nubwo hari ibihuha bivuga ko abantu benshi banduye muri Irani, ku ya 28 Gashyantare ibihugu birenga icumi byasubije abanduye muri Irani, bivuga ko ubwandu bushobora kuba buruta cyane 388 leta ya Irani yari yatangaje icyo gihe.
Inteko Ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho abayigize 23 muri 290 bayanduye tariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza muri Irani kurekura ku gahato abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo mu buryo buzira amakimbirane, ndetse no kurekura burundu abandi bose bafunzwe.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira kw'icyorezo mu bigo byafunze, nk'ahantu ho kwita ku barwayi, aho ubuvuzi bw'ibanze butaba buhari.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, guverinoma ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari cyo gipimo cyo hejuru cy'abantu bapfuye mu munsi umwe mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Abantu bagera kuri 12 bari abanyapolitiki cyangwa abahoze ari bo muri leta ya Irani bapfuye bazize iki cyorezo kuva ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yagaragazaga ko buri saha havukaga abantu 50 banduye coronavirus, kandi buri minota 10 hakaga umuntu umwe wapfuye azize coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, abanduye muri Irani bashobora kuba baruta abavuzwe inshuro eshanu.
Byongeye kandi, byasabwe ko Amerika yakumira Irani mu rwego rwo gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu by'igihugu mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano ku bukungu bw'ibihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo byashyirwa mu bikorwa, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyatangajwe mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abakerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bagaragayeho ko banduye SARS-CoV-2.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zivuye cyangwa zijya mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma y'aho, habonetse itsinda ry'abantu banduye COVID-19 batarabonana, aho abanduye 16 batangiye kugaragara muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yasohoye itegeko rishya rigamije gukumira icyorezo, harimo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Gusipe Conte yagize ati "Aho bakwirakwijwe, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizongera gukorwa".
Gahunda yo guhagarika ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino muri utwo turere yarategetswe. "Ku ya 4 Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza mu gihugu bifungwa burundu nyuma y'uko Ubutaliyani bugeze ku bantu 100 bapfuye.
Ibikorwa byose by'imikino, harimo n'umupira w'amaguru wa Serie A, bizakomeza gukorwa nta nkomyi kugeza muri Mata, ariko guhera ku ya 9 Werurwe, siporo zose zizahagarikwa by'agateganyo nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Gusepi Konte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarara uretse amasoko makuru na farumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Ubuvuzi, Kuboneza, Kuboneza no kugenzura (SIAARTI) ryatanze inama z'itsinda ry'abaganga ku ngamba zishobora gufatwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwaje imbere y'u Bushinwa mu kugira umubare munini w'abantu bishwe na coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutangaza abantu 3,405 bamaze guhitanwa na yo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege z'intambara icyenda zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bari bamaze kwandura, 15,887 barapfuye naho 21,815 barakize, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu ntara ya Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yavuze ko umubare munini w'abaturage bakuze mu Butaliyani ndetse no kuba nta bushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye umubare munini w'abapfuye.
Ubwongereza bwagize icyo buvuga kuri coronavirus bwabanje kuba kimwe mu bihugu byagize ingaruka zikomeye, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza nta mabwiriza yo kwirinda kwegerana cyangwa akumira abantu mu ngo yari yarashyizeho.
Ibyo byatumye leta inengwa ko yananiwe gukemura impungenge abaturage bari bafite. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yasohoye itangazo rivuga ku ngendo zose n'ibindi bibazo by'imibereho, asaba abantu gukorera mu rugo no kwirinda ahantu nko mu tubyiniro, muri resitora no mu mazu y'imyidagaduro.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho kwidagadura, nko mu tubyiniro no mu mazu y'imyidagaduro, hagomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya ko izatanga 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi, kugeza ku mafaranga 2500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri mu gihe cy'icyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ko hashyirwaho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda kwegerana, guhagarika guteranira hamwe kw'abantu barenga babiri no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze kugeza igihe bibaye ngombwa.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uburyo bwari busanzwe, iyi myanzuro yashyizweho n'abapolisi mu rwego rwo gukumira no gusakaza imyigaragambyo.
Yabujije ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose gufunga, uretse gusa ibifatwa nk'ibikenewe, nka za supermarket, farumasi, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibyuma, za peteroli n'amaduka y'imodoka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umurwayi wa mbere wa COVID-19 muri Pacific Northwest muri leta ya Washington yemejwe ko ari umugabo wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Ku ya 29 Mutarama, itsinda rya White House Coronavirus Team ryashinzwe.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange, kandi buhagarika ingendo z'abinjira mu gihugu baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara - ikigo cy'ingenzi gishinzwe ubuzima rusange muri guverinoma ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byo gupima.
Nubwo byakozwe, Amerika yatangiye isuzuma buhoro buhoro, bituma igipimo cy'ubwandu nyakuri kitagaragara.
