Ibigo byashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo z'abakozi, bifata impapuro z'umwanzuro, kandi bishishikariza abakozi gukorera mu ngo.
Ibirori n'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko ingendo mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse u Bwongereza, zizahagarikwa mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
