Bamwe mu banyeshuri ba Sene bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bahuriye hamwe mu kohereza imfashanyo mu turere turimo Sene, hamwe n'itsinda rinini ry'umuryango w'akarere ka Chicago ryasohotsemo raporo y'igice yohereje udupfukamunwa 50,000 N95 mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei ku ya 30/1 . Ishyirahamwe ry'urukundo ryo kohereza imfashanyo ryahise ryitangira, rifatanyije na FedEx, kohereza udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwitonzi, birimo imyenda n'ibisate, mu modoka yo mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze yoherejwe ku bitaro bya Wan Wan Wan Wan kuri 30/1 .
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga agashimwe ka miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku muntu wese uzatanga urukingo n'umuti bizatuma "abaturage bo muri Afurika no mu majyepfo ya Aziya barokoka akaga".
