Kugira ngo wirinde ikwirakwizwa ry'iyi virusi, ni byiza gukaraba intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti wica udukoko ku ntoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'udukoko mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu yo gusukura intoki mu gihe umuntu yaba yiyuhagira ku ncuro ya mbere ari 20 ku ijana. Iyo mibare yo kwiyuhagira mu gihe umuntu yaba yiyuhagira ku ncuro ya mbere yageraga kuri 35 ku ijana.
Gucana intoki n'isukari ikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki n'isabune irwanya indwara zikomoka kuri za mikorobe, byatanze ingaruka zikubye inshuro eshatu ku rugero rw'indwara z'ibyorezo ziterwa na mikorobe ziva mu kurya kurusha izo zituruka mu gukaraba n'isukari ikoreshwa mu gukemura indwara. Gupima intoki ukoresheje isabune ikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki n'isukari ikoreshwa mu gukemura indwara zikomoka kuri za mikorobe, byatanze igipimo cy'amasegonda 30 y'isuku.
Ariko isabune n'amazi bifite ubushobozi buruta ubw'isuku yo gukaraba intoki ku ngufu mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1. Virusi na fungi ya Clostridium ku ntoki. Imirimo yo guteza imbere isuku yo gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'ubuzima ishobora guteza imbere uburezi bw'itsinda ryo gukaraba intoki, kongera kubona umuti ukaraba intoki w'ibinyobwa bisindisha, no kwandika amabwiriza yo gukaraba intoki.
Hakenewe ubundi bushakashatsi ku mikorere y'ubuvuzi butandukanye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune byemezwa ko ari uburyo bw'ibanze bwo gutuma umuntu agira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse no kurya neza.
Icyakora, kuba nta mazi, isabune cyangwa imashini zo gukaraba intoki zihagije mu ngo z'abaturage, mu mashuri no mu kazi, byatumye habaho ubukangurambaga bwo kugeza isuku ku isi.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro bya Afurika, nta tubari tw'amaboko dufite hafi y'ubwiherero rusange cyangwa ubw'abantu ku giti cyabo, nubwo hari uburyo bwo gukora imiterere y'amaboko.
Ariko, kudahana intoki kenshi bishobora kuba ingaruka z'imyitwarire idakwiriye bitewe n'ubuke bw'isabune n'amazi.
Kwiyongera no gukwirakwiza ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki mu buryo burangwa n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki no gutuma abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu benshi bahora bakaraba intoki.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigirweho, hakenewe kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Gusuzuma ubuvugizi ku bushakashatsi bwa siyansi 70 byagaragaje ko uburyo bw'imibereho myiza ari bwo bufite ingaruka nziza mu gukwirakwiza gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, mu gihe ubukangurambaga mu gukwirakwiza ibikorwa by'imibereho myiza bw'abaturage bufite ingaruka nke. Urugero rw'uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu mashuri bwakozwe na UNICEF (Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu) ishishikariza amashuri gufata ingamba, ingamba zidahenze zo kwemeza ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki n'isabune mu zindi nshingano z'isuku.
Iyo amanota make amaze kugerwaho, amashuri ashobora guhindurwa kuva ku nyenyeri imwe kugera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka iri shuri ry'intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo kongera umubare w'abana bakaraba intoki byashyizwe mu bikorwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubwandu n'impfu by'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba Intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukaraba intoki bugamije guhindura imyitwarire. Nk'ingaruka y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cy'umwaka wa 2019-2020, UNICEF yasohoye imbonerahamwe yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwagaragaje ko mu bihugu byateye imbere, gukaraba intoki byemewe cyane kubera ko DALY itabyemerewe.
Ariko, hari ubushakashatsi bwatanze igitekerezo cy'uko kongera isabune mu gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro cyane kurusha amazi n'ibindi bikoresho by'isuku.
Ingaruka zo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'umuntu - cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere iteye ubwoba nko kuba ari ababyeyi babyaye cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro - byatangajwe bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abavumbuzi babiri b'isuku y'intoki: Umuganga w'Umudage Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreye i Vienne, muri Otirishiya na Florence Nightingale, wavumbuye uburyo bwo kugenzura mu cyongereza.
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bakomeje kwizera ko indwara z'ibyorezo ari zo zitera impumuro mbi, zitwa impumuro mbi z'ibishwi.
Mu 1980, Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko gukaraba intoki ari uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda kwandura.
Icyorezo cya virusi ya Influenza y'ingurube mu 2009 na COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye abantu bo mu bihugu byinshi barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
Urugero, inyandiko "Imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye" iri iruhande rw'intoki z'abanduye yashyizwe mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'ibiro by'amazu manini n'ibibuga by'indege mu Budage.
Ijambo "gukaraba intoki" risobanura "guhamagarira umuntu ufite ubuzima bwiza" kugira ngo abe umukozi w'ikintu runaka cyangwa kugira uruhare muri cyo.
Ibi byaturutse ku mwandiko w'Ivanjiri ya Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yakarabye ibiganza mu gihe cy'urubanza rwo kubamba Yezu, ariko ni amagambo yakoreshejwe cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'Icyongereza.
Muri Macbeth Insinzi, Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu kugerageza kwiyezaho igitekerezo cyanduye, yumva icyaha yakoze n'umugore we yagerageje kumuhindura.
Byagaragaye ko abantu bamaze kubona ko hari ingeso mbi, bakunze kwiyambaza gukaraba intoki kurusha ikindi kintu cyose, bakunze kwiyambaza ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza cyane, ntibakunze gukora ibikorwa by'isuku, urugero nko gukora ibikorwa by'ubutabazi.
Amadini asobanura ko gukaraba intoki ari ikintu cyo kwiyeza kandi ko ari ikimenyetso. Gukaraba intoki, nk'ikimenyetso cyo gukaraba, ni ugukoresha amazi aho gukoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ni kimwe mu biranga umugenzo wo gukaraba intoki mu madini menshi, nka Bahai, Hindu, Tevila na Netilate Yadaim mu idini rya Kiyahudi, Lavabo mu idini rya Gikristo, n'ubuhindu mu idini rya Isilamu.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, basabwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero.
Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, na bo basabwa gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya.
Ibikorwa byo gukumira ibyago byo mu kazi bya COVID-19
Gucunga ibyangiritse mu kazi mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19 ni gahunda yo gushyiraho ingamba z'ubuziranenge n'iz'ubuzima mu rwego rwo gukumira ibyangiritse mu kwirinda icyorezo cya koronavirusi ya 2019 (COVID-19)
Uburyo bukwiye bwo kwirinda ibyago by'indwara ku kazi bushingiye ku gace k'akazi n'akazi, hashingiwe ku kaga kazanywe n'akazi, ku buremere bw'indwara mu baturage no ku ngaruka zishobora guterwa n'abakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora guhangana na COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'Ubuyobozi bw'Umutekano n'Iterambere ry'Umurimo (OSHA), kwirinda ibyago by'akazi bigira ingaruka ku bantu bose n'abakozi bo mu bigo, bityo rero, uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kwirinda ubwandu bw'indwara bwashyizweho, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye cyangwa bafite ibibazo byo guhumeka, no gukora isuku isanzwe yo mu kazi no gukaraba no guhumanya.
Ibyago byo mu rwego rwo hejuru mu kazi ni ibyo gusaba abantu kwirinda guhura n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye bitewe n'ingendo z'abantu benshi cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Aha harimo abakozi bakorana n'abaturage muri rusange, nko mu mashuri, mu bikorwa byo mu rwego rwo hejuru, mu nganda no mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'indege.
Kugenzura ibyago by'iyi mitwe, harimo no kwirinda ubwandu, harimo guhumeka neza hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'imiti yica udukoko n'imyenda ikingira, no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'ubuzima mu gihe umuntu yaba afite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bakora mu by'ubuvuzi n'abakora mu byumba by'indembe bafite ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, kandi ko ibyago biba byinshi cyane iyo bakoresheje ibyuma byo guhumeka cyangwa bakusanya ibipimo by'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19.
Kugabanya ibyago ku buryo bukwiriye ku bakozi bakora mu rwego rw'ubwubatsi bw'ubugenzuzi nk'icyumba cy'ihindagurika ry'umwuka w'agahinda no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye bikwiye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka zitandukanye ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kureka akazi kubera ko bafite ibyago byo kurwara, bakeneye kwita ku bandi, cyangwa batinya kurwara.
Abafatanyabikorwa mu bucuruzi bashobora guhindura ibyifuzo by'ibicuruzwa bisabwa n'impamvu yo kubisaba (urugero, kugurisha igihe abantu baje kugura cyangwa gutanga cyangwa kugurisha ibintu by'inyongera).
Mu bihe bya vuba, ubwato bw'ubwikorezi mu turere twazahajwe na COVID-19 bushobora guhagarikwa.Ibyorezo byanduza bishobora kuba byarateganyijwe kandi gahunda yo kwirinda ishobora gukoreshwa mu bikorwa byo kurinda.
Iyi gahunda igaragaza ingamba z'ibyago bijyanye n'aho virusi itera indwara n'akazi, harimo aho umuntu yanduye, imiterere y'ibyago mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago ku muntu ku giti cye nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara z'igihe kirekire.
Bavuga kandi ko hakenewe ingamba zo guhangana n'ibyago no gutegura uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibihe bishobora gutuma icyorezo gikomeza gukwirakwira.
Imyiteguro n'amabwiriza yo kwirinda indwara zandura bishobora kuba ikibazo cy'amategeko y'igihugu n'ay'ibihugu.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo ni ukugabanya ubwandu mu itsinda, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura no kugabanya ingaruka ku bandi barwayi mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Uko ubwandu bwiyongera mu baturage, ni na ko ibisubizo byagiye byigwa.
Kuzamura igenga ibyago ni igitekerezo gikoreshwa cyane mu bikorwa byo kurinda no kubungabunga umutekano w'itsinda ry'abashinzwe kugenzura ibyago n'ibikorwa.
Iyo ubwandu bwa COVID-19 butaragerwaho, ingamba zikoreshwa cyane ni ingamba z'ubwubatsi, zikurikirwa n'ingamba z'ubuziranenge n'imiti n'ibindi bikoresho byo kwirinda.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubwubatsi burimo kwirinda kw'abakozi kwangirika bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'umukozi kandi birashobora kuba igisubizo cyiza cyo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Abayobozi bakuru b'imirimo bahindura imikorere y'akazi cyangwa intambwe zisaba abakozi kugira icyo bakora.
Imyenda y'ubwirinzi (PPE) ni ingirakamaro cyane ugereranyije n'uburyo bwo kurwanya indwara, ariko ishobora gufasha mu kwirinda indwara.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba kugenwa hashingiwe ku ngaruka zishobora guterwa n'abakozi, kugenwa mu buryo bukwiriye nk'uko bikorwa (urugero, guhumeka nabi), kugenwa igihe cyaryo, kugenwa mu buryo bwemewe, gukoreshwa igihe kirekire, gusimbuzwa, gukurwaho igihe ari ngombwa, gusukurwa, kubikwa cyangwa gutegurwa kugira ngo hatagira ubwandu.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'ikigo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye gishinzwe umutekano n'umutekano (OSHA), ibyago byo mu kazi bifite aho bihuriye cyane n'abantu ku giti cyabo n'abakozi bo mu bigo.
Yasabye ko ahantu hose hakorerwa ibikorwa byose hakwiye gukaraba intoki cyane cyane no gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye cyangwa bafite ibibazo byo guhumeka, harimo inkorora, guhumeka nabi, gutanga imyanda, kwitegura guhanagura cyangwa guhanagura imyenda niba ari ngombwa, kubwira abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho no gukurikirana no gukurikiza gahunda yo gusukura no guhumeka aho bakorera.
Gushishikariza abantu kumenya no kwirinda abanduye ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bari mu kazi.
Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatangaje ko abakozi bagaragaza ibimenyetso bagomba kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bamaze gukira indwara, ibimenyetso by'indwara n'ibindi bimenyetso by'indwara mu gihe cy'amasaha nibura 24 nta miti cyangwa ibindi bikoresho, kandi igihe cyose indwara itarushaho gukomera, abakozi bagombye kuguma mu rugo bakita ku bagize imiryango yabo barwaye, kandi abakozi batagomba kubwirwa iby'ingamba.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na OSHA, akazi k'ibanze gashyirwamo ibyago ni ako umuntu ashobora kugirana n'umuntu ufite uburebure bwa metero 6 (1.8m) ariko akaba adafite cyangwa akekwaho kuba afite COVID-19, ariko akaba ashobora kuba yanduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko yanduye mu bantu cyangwa bitewe n'uko umuntu yagiye mu mahanga ahantu hari COVID-19.
Aba bakozi barimo abakozi bafite aho bahurira na rusange, nko mu mashuri, aho bakorera mu nganda cyangwa aho bacuruza. Gutegereza inzego z'ubwubatsi ku bijyanye n'ibi n'imiryango y'ibiza birimo gushyiraho filteri zigezweho zo guhumeka no kongera umubare w'ibyuma bihumura no gushyiraho inzitizi z'ubuvuzi nk'imirasire ya plastiki yo gukingira no gushyiraho serivisi yo kuzana imyanya y'igorofa. Abayobozi bashinzwe ibi n'imiryango y'ibiza bashishikariza abakozi barwaye kuva mu ngo zabo, guhuza abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'ibiyobyabwenge, gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibiza no kwirinda ibiyobyabwenge bidakenewe mu gihe COVID-19 ikwirakwira, guteganya gahunda yo kwirinda no kwirinda COVID-19, gushyiraho imyenda y'akazi, gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda no kwirinda COVID-19 mu kazi, gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda COVID-19 zishobora guteza akaga, no gutoza abakozi no kwirinda COVID-19, gushyiraho amategeko yo kwirinda no kwirinda COVID-19 mu kazi, no gutoza abakozi no mu bikorwa by'ubuzima, no mu rwego rwo kwirinda COVID-19.
Abakozi bo muri izo nzego z'ibyago ntibakunze gusabwa gukoresha ibyuma bifasha abafite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Niba umuntu arwaye ku kibuga cy'indege, igenzura rikwiriye rishobora gukoreshwa mu kurinda abakozi n'abagenzi harimo gutandukanya umurwayi n'abandi bantu bagera kuri metero 6 no gushyiraho umwe mu itsinda ryo kwita ku murwayi, guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa gusaba kurinda umunwa no gukingiriza umunwa umurwayi igihe yisinziriye cyangwa asoma.
Itsinda ry'abakozi rigomba kwambara uturindantoki tw'ubutabazi igihe cyose bahuye n'umushoferi urwaye cyangwa bahuye n'imyanda y'umubiri cyangwa imyanda, kandi bakongerera ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku giti cyabo mu gihe umushoferi arwaye afite ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero cyangwa igihumeka gikomeye.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bigomba kuba biri mu dufuka twa plastike, kandi ibyangiritse bigomba gukurwaho no kwanduzwa. Ku masoko aremereye, harimo ingendo zo guhaha no gutwara abagenzi, kugenzura ibyangiritse harimo gusubika ingendo mugihe urwaye cyangwa kwinjizwa mu kato k'umuntu ku giti cye no kumenyesha ihuriro ry'abaganga ku bwato niba umuntu afite ibicurane cyangwa ibimenyetso ku bwato.
Ubusanzwe, ubuvuzi bugomba kuboneka hafi y'umuntu uri mu kato. Amashuri, ibigo byita ku bana na CDC bishobora gutanga igihe gito cyo kwanduza abantu cyangwa kubangamira abakora isuku mu gihe umuntu wanduye ari mu kigo cy'ishuri, bitewe n'uko mu baturage hashobora kuba hari abantu benshi.
Iyo nta ngamba zihari zo kugabanya ingendo rusange, uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu bushobora gukoreshwa, nko gusiba ingendo, amateraniro n'ibindi bikorwa by'abantu benshi nk'inyigisho z'ubuvuzi, amateraniro y'idini cyangwa gusangira muri cafeteria, kongera igihe hagati y'ameza no gutegura ingendo n'ikiruhuko by'abanyeshuri, no gusiba ingendo z'abakozi batagomba kujya mu kazi, no gukoresha ahantu h'ibiro by'abaganga ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bya virusi ya virusi ya SIDA.
Iyo hari ubwandu bukomeye mu baturage, nubwo uburyo bwo kwirinda bw'abantu buhari, ikiruhuko cy'ibiruhuko ku mashuri gishobora gutekerezwaho. Ku bijyanye n'itegeko ry'ibiro by'ishami rigena ko ibikorwa bya buri munsi bigomba gukorwa mu buryo bw'abantu benshi, ibyago by'ubuzima ntibikwiye kwitabwaho na CDC.
Abacunga umutekano bagomba guhura n'abantu banduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 barasabwa gukurikiza uburyo bwo kwivuza mu buryo bwihuse, harimo no kwambara ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Niba hari guhura hafi mu gihe cy'umutwaro wangiza, abakozi bagomba gusukura imodoka zabo no gusukura no gusukura ibikoresho byo kongera gukoresha, bakoresheje ibikoresho byo gusukura inzu, bakoresheje ibikoresho byo gusukura inzu, bakoresha uburyo bwo gusukura. Gukoresha PPE nke no gukaraba no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ivuga ko abakora mu bigo by'ubuzima n'iby'ubuvuzi bw'indembe bari mu kaga gakomeye.
Imirimo iteje akaga irimo gutanga serivisi z'ubuvuzi, ubufasha, gukora ibizamini by'ubuvuzi no kujyana abaganga ku bakozi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Abo bakozi baba bafite ibyago byinshi iyo bakoresha ibyuma bihumeka umwuka cyangwa bagatoranya ibipimo by'abantu banduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Ibikoresho byo guhanahana umwuka w'umuyoboro w'umwuka w'imbere mu muhogo, ibikoresho byo gutera akabariro, ibikoresho byo gusuzuma umuyoboro w'umwuka, hamwe n'ibikoresho byo gusuzuma amenyo no gusuzuma cyangwa kuvura ibipimo.
Ibyago byo gukora mu byumba by'imva birimo kuba abakozi bategura imihango y'ihamba barwaye COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; abo bakozi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura COVID-19 igihe batwaye inkingo, ingamba z'ubwubatsi zinyuranye zashyizweho muri izo nzego z'ibyago zirimo kuba ibyumba by'ubwiherero by'abarwayi bafite cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, igihe bakoresha imashini z'ubuhumekero.
Imashini z'umuvuduko w'umwuka mubi zishobora kuba nziza muri gahunda zimwe na zimwe z'ubuvuzi no mu gihe cyo gupfa.
Ibipimo bigomba gukorwa n'imashini yo ku rwego rwa 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, OMS, rihamagarira abarwayi kwirinda ahantu hategerejwe gukorerwa ibizamini bya COVID-19.
Muri ONU, NIOSH mask N95 igezweho cyangwa nziza igomba gukoreshwa mu bigo bya leta, gahunda yo kwirinda ibibazo byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikurikirana ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, amahugurwa n'ibizamini byo kwa muganga.
Ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bwo guhumeka byongereye ubwirinzi n'iterambere mu by'ubuvuzi. OMS ntishyigikira ikoreshwa ry'imyambaro yo guhumeka nk'uko bimeze ku ndwara yo mu buhumekero ya COVID-19 ariko ishobora kwandura mu buryo bw'imyanda.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abantu bakorerwa ibizamini by'ubuvuzi bambara udupfukamunwa two mu rwego rwo kubaga gusa.
Ku bantu bafashe ibizamini by'ubuhumekero mu gihe bakorera mu bitaro cyangwa mu ngendo z'abarwaye COVID-19 badafite ibyuma bihumanya umwuka, OMS isaba abantu kwambara agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo, udupfukamunwa tw'imbere n'utundi tw'imbere, n'udupfukamunwa tw'imbere n'udupfukamunwa tw'imbere.
Iyo bakoresheje ibyuma byo guhumeka, udupfukamunwa two mu cyumba cyo kwa muganga tuba N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Urebye uko imbangukiragutabara za PPE zishyirwa mu bikorwa, OMS isaba ko hakurwaho ibisabwa bya PPE kugira ngo abantu babashe gutanga amakuru, ko hakurwaho inzitizi z'ubuvuzi nk'amadirishya yo kwa muganga, ko hakwemererwa gusa abantu bafite aho bahuriye n'abaganga mu gihe barembeje abarwayi ba COVID-19, ko hakoreshwa gusa ibikoresho bya PPE mu gihe cy'akazi runaka, ko hakomeza gukoreshwa ibikoresho bimwe by'ubuhumekero mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi, ko hakomeza gukoreshwa uburyo bwo gusuzuma indwara, gukurikirana no gushyira kuri gahunda gahunda gahunda z'imfashanyigisho za PPE, no gukoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe umuntu adafite ibimenyetso.
