Umuti uvura angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ni umuti uvura impyiko z'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu maraso, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ibuza ingirabuzimafatizo za angiotensin-α-cycloroquine (ACE) ikora mu kugabanya ubukana bwa angiotensin ya kabiri no kongera Ang1-7, bituma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ishobora kuba inzira yinjira muri za virusi za koronavirusi.
Igisubizo cy'umuntu kuri iki kimenyetso cy'ubushakashatsi cy'imiti gikunze kugaragara nka hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya zinc ya metali igaragara ku gice cy'imbere cy'ingingo z'umubiri.
ACE2 igizwe n'indangamuntu yo mu gice cya N cy'indangamuntu ya peptidase M2 n'indangamuntu yo mu gice cya C ihujwe na aside ya amine y'indangamuntu y'ikirenga.
ACE ni ubwoko bumwe bw'ubwoko bwa I-protein, hamwe na enzyme yayo ikora kuri selile receptor ku ruhu rw'umutsi ndetse no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
Iyo ingirabuzimafatizo yavuye muri ACE2 ikanyura mu furonore ya furonore, iyo furonore ikaba ingirabuzimafatizo yitwa shades, ikaba furonore y'umwimerere mu maraso kandi ikajya mu musatsi.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ikora ku mitsi y'umubiri, cyane cyane mu bwoko bwa C bw'ingirabuzimafatizo ya cycloid ya kabiri, mu mara mato, mu mitsi y'ingingo z'amaraso, mu mitsi y'amaraso no mu mitsi y'amaraso mu ngingo nyinshi.
ACE2 ifata kandi imiterere ya mRNA mu gice cy'imbere cy'ubwonko, no mu gice cy'ubwonko hagati, no mu gice cy'ubwonko bw'imbere, no mu gice cy'ubwonko bw'imbere.
Igikorwa cyambere cya ACE2 ni uguhuza ingano ya ACE.
ACE ni hormone yitwa aniotensin A ikora nk'uko ingo-A ikora.
ACE2 ikora mu gihe cy'imiterere ya carboxyl-termial amino acid phenylalanine ituruka kuri anigotensin II (Asp-Arg-Bal-Tyr-IIe-His-Pro-Phe) kandi ikora hydrolyses mu cyayi cy'ubushake bwa angiotensin (1 - 7, (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Lle-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi guteranya indi peptides nyinshi, nka -[des-Arg9] bradykinin, apelin neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itera ubudahangarwa bwa amino acide SLC6A19 ikora kandi iboneka mu ndwara ya Hartnap.
Nk'impuzandengo y'ubwandu, ACE2 ikora nk'inzira y'ibanze yo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za virusi zimwe na zimwe, nka HcoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (iyo virusi iteza SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (iyo virusi iteza COVID-19).
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, guhererekanya S1 ya poroteyine ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ya ACE2 ya enzymes y'urusobe ku ruhu rw'ingirabuzima, bigira ingaruka zo guhindura igiteranyo kinini cy'imiterere ya virusi na enzymes mu ngirabuzima.
Hari impungenge ko kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya iyi ndwara.
Ariko, hari amatsinda y'abahanga mu by'imibonano mpuzabitsina n'abakora siporo yo kwisiga bagendera ku ihame ryo kugabanya ACE no kugabanya ARB.
Icyiciro cy'ibanze cy'ibarura n'ibisobanuro by'ibisobanuro byatanzwe mu Gashyantare 11, 2020, aho byerekanye ko "ikoreshwa rya ACE ryatera imbere ryongereye uburemere bwa 34% mu kugabanya ibyago byo kurwara indwara ugereranyije n'inteko".
"Ikindi kandi, ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'ibihaha bikomeye byari bigabanyutse mu barwayi bavurwaga ACEs, ariko ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'ibihaha byariyongereye, cyane cyane ku barwaye indwara z'umutima, cyane cyane abafite ikibazo cy'ihungabana ry'umutima no kudakora neza kw'umutima".
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byafashije mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero zirimo nimunoniya ifitanye isano na kanseri, nubwo ingaruka zabaye mbi cyane kurusha izindi ngaruka z'indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya muntu (rhACE2) igomba kuba umuti mushya ku gikomere gikomeye cy'ibihaha, kandi yagaragaje ko ishobora guhangana n'amaraso yo mu bihaha no kubura umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube ntoyi hamwe na lipopysaccharide- byatsinze mu bimenyetso bikomeye by'ubuhumekero bwinshi.
Ikirenga igihe cyo gupfa cya ErhACe mu bantu ni hafi amasaha 10, igihe cyo gukora ni iminota 30, naho igihe cyo gukora ni amasaha 24.
