Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu zigendanwa zigenewe gufasha abantu gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi cya 2019-20, urugero nko kumenya abantu (abo mu gihe runaka) bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Porogaramu nyinshi zagiye zikoreshwa, ndetse na leta z'ibihugu zimwe na zimwe zagiye zifasha mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko.
Bimwe mu bikorwa by'ibanze byakozwe mu kubaka imikoranire ya porogaramu.
