Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko byasangiye imbaraga mu gufasha porogaramu za Bluetooth zisanzwe gukora neza kuri Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'u Bushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipo, yatangije porogaramu igenewe abaturage, ibemerera kubaza niba hari umuntu wigeze afatwa na COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, porogaramu yitwa Tresse Towers ikoreshwa.
Porogaramu yateguwe, ishyirwaho kandi izashyirwa mu bikorwa na sosiyete ya IT, kandi igiye gushyikirizwa guverinoma. Porogaramu y'intangiriro ya "Stop Coronavirus" ya Macedonia y'amajyaruguru ni porogaramu y'ibanze yo gutahura abantu banduye no gutanga ibisubizo byihuse mu bigo nderabuzima.
Porogaramu yashyizweho na Minisiteri y'Ikoranabuhanga n'Itumanaho na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari ku murongo wo kwemerwa kuri Google Play Store no mu bubiko bwa Apple.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko gahunda yo kwishyura serivisi ari imwe mu zigezweho, kandi ko izaboneka mu gihe cy'icyumweru. Ibisa n'ibyo biteganijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa.
Australia na New Zealand byombi birateganya gukurikiza gahunda yo gukurikirana Singapore na Bluetooth. Uburusiya bugiye gushyiraho gahunda yo gukurikirana abarwayi basuzumwe COVID-19 baba i Moscou, yagenewe kwemeza ko abarwayi batasiba iwabo.
Ross Anderson, injeniyeri y'ubucunga muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari ibibazo bishobora kubaho mu mikorere y'ibanze, harimo amakosa y'inyungu, kandi ko bishoboka cyane ko byagira ingaruka mbi iyo porogaramu igabanijwe ku gice gito cy'abaturage.
Mu rwego rwo kugaragaza impungenge z'uko porogaramu za "coronavirus" zishobora kubura cyangwa gukwirakwira, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongera porogaramu zimeze nka coronavirus ku Ububiko bwa Apple.Ibi ni "ibisanzwe" gusa kandi birashoboka ko ari ibirimo ibirimo kumenyekana.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abateye ibi bitero by'umwihariko bagaragaje impungenge ku bibazo by'ubufatanye mu gukurikirana icyorezo cya coronavirus, cyane cyane niba ubugenzuzi bwitondewe bw'ibikorwaremezo byubatswe mu rwego rwo guhangana na coronavirus buzashoboka igihe cyose ibyago bizaba byarangiye.
