Hari urwego rw'ubushakashatsi ku by'umutekano rwatejwe imbere, harimo:
ADN na RNA (Icyiciro cya 1 cy'iterambere n'urukingo rw'amahitamo: moderna, mRNA-1273)
Virusi igenewe (Icyiciro cya 1 cy'abakoraga n'inkingo zatoranyijwe: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus ubwoko bwa 5 bw'igishushanyo mbonera).
Nkuko byatangajwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI mu kwezi kwa kane, muri rusange, porogaramu 115 zatoranyijwe mu ntangiriro z'iterambere, 78 zashyizwe mu bikorwa nk'imishinga ikora (79 nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cya Milken), naho izindi 37 zitangajwe, ariko amakuru y'abantu bose aracyari make (niba bateganya cyangwa se bateguye).
