Igisasu cy'ubwirinzi gikoreshwa mu kuvura no kuvura ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bw'abantu bakira COVID-19 kugira ngo kijye mu bantu bagenewe gukingirwa mu gihe hari uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara.
Iki gikorwa cyageragejwe kuri SARS ariko nta gisubizo gihari.
Virusi ihuriza hamwe ni uburyo bushoboka bwo gukemura ibibazo byibuza bw'ubwirinzi bw'ubwirinzi ku bakandida ba SARS-CoV-2.
Ubundi buryo, nk'ubundi buryo bwo kwanduza umuntu, cyangwa uburyo bwo kwanduza bakteria, bushobora kuba ari bwo bukenewe.
Andi mabwiriza yo kuvura indwara zidakira, urugero nk'imiti ikora nk'imiti yo kuvura indwara zidakira, irimo iterambere.
Mu bikomoka ku mikorobe, harimo poroteyine zo mu maraso y'abarwayi bakira indwara, hamwe n'ubwirinzi bwihariye bwa virusi bushobora kongerwa kugira ngo byihutishe ikwirakwira ryayo.
Indwara ziterwa na koronavirusi ni itsinda ry'indwara ziterwa n'ibimenyetso rusange.
Li Wenliang, umuganga mukuru w'ibitaro by'i Wan, yaje kwandura COVID-19 hanyuma ahita apfa nyuma yo kumenyekana ko iyi virusi yageze mu bantu benshi.
